<div style='font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;'>
  <h1 style='color: #333;'>Verify Your Email, {{name}}</h1>
  <p>Thank you for signing up for Wordz! Please verify your email address to complete your
    registration.</p>
  <p>Here is your code for email verification :</p>
  <div
    style='background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;'
  >
    <p style='font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 5px; color: #333; margin: 0;'><strong
      >{{code}}</strong></p>
  </div>
  <p>This code will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.</p>
  <p>Best regards,<br />The Wordz Team</p>
</div>